    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/5c654901b786c6c593bd011163c83586.poster.avif?t=1759889582\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/5c654901b786c6c593bd011163c83586.webm?t=1759889582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>身为无名者，一名被万神之父亲自选中的有罪之人，你的命运岌岌可危。是守护这个行将就木的世界还是摧毁它，选择全在于你。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/d7ed7e7265fe5b316d9d0e77af30c2f2.poster.avif?t=1759889582\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/d7ed7e7265fe5b316d9d0e77af30c2f2.webm?t=1759889582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>无望者、迷失者、淹毙者和被遗忘者，所有人都只遵循一条规则：为了生存而战斗。死灵谷的每个阴暗角落里都潜伏着无数代罪犯与恶人们的后裔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/ee938c4370cd4c4f55bd6dcf1a727def.poster.avif?t=1759889582\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/ee938c4370cd4c4f55bd6dcf1a727def.webm?t=1759889582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>死灵谷中到处都是殒命于此的人们所留下的强大遗物。收集这些武器、铠甲、盾牌、法杖、珠宝、图腾、帽子、书本和其他物什，追随他们的脚步吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/5774852fbf3e2cd453e2013a9786c7a0.poster.avif?t=1759889582\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717090/extras/5774852fbf3e2cd453e2013a9786c7a0.webm?t=1759889582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>在你的旅程中，你将遇见其他被囚者们。他们因何罪过或失败而来到死灵谷，有他们自己的理由。可是你最好不要往下评判，因为你可能会发现，为了活下去，你也时常会需要依赖这些陌生和困苦的卑微者们。<br><br>",
